\doxysubsection{Detailed Description}
The \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_cell_value_proxy}{XLCell\+Value\+Proxy}} class is used for proxy (or placeholder) objects for \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_cell_value}{XLCell\+Value}} objects. 

The \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_cell_value_proxy}{XLCell\+Value\+Proxy}} class is used for proxy (or placeholder) objects for \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_cell_value}{XLCell\+Value}} objects. The purpose is to enable implicit conversion during assignment operations. \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_cell_value_proxy}{XLCell\+Value\+Proxy}} objects can not be constructed manually by the user, only through \mbox{\hyperlink{class_open_x_l_s_x_1_1_x_l_cell}{XLCell}} objects.
